<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10645] TestKMS fails because race condition writing acl files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10645</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;TestKMS#testACLs()&lt;/tt&gt; test randomly fails because a race condition while updating the acls files which is hot-reloaded.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should disable the background thread that does the reload and do it manually for the purposes of the test.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
